# Boards beta

Boards with ad hoc cards are available to all users, and we are excited to open additional features (including cards connected to Adobe Workfront tasks and issues) for public beta beginning in June 2022.

Adobe Workfront Boards are flexible tools that allow team collaboration by providing access to a shared board that contains columns and cards.

For general information about boards, see [Boards overview](/help/quicksilver/agile/boards-overview.md).

## Release schedule

* Public beta launch: June 2022
* Official release: July 2022

